title: Vampire Volleyball v1.0.0
description:
The wackiest volleyball game to ever hit Android is here!

These vampires are "dead" set on winning a volleyball tournament just for the creatures of the night!

Battle your way through all the opponents to win the coveted Vampire Cup!

Features:

-1 or 2 player action
-8 unique vampires, each with their own special move
-3 different heroes, with unique jumps, kicks, and spikes
-Easy single button game play, or full d-pad movement
-Fluid animations and a rocking soundtrack
